1. Moj prijatelj *baca* loptu. (My friend is throwing a ball.)
2. Kada *bacim* novčić, uvek biram glavu. (When I toss a coin, I always choose heads.)
3. On *baca* smeće u kantu za đubre. (He throws trash in the garbage can.)
4. Da li možeš da mi *baciš* olovku? (Can you throw me a pen?)
5. U ovoj igri, cilj je *baciti* kuglu što dalje. (In this game, the goal is to throw the ball as far as possible.)
6. Ja ću *baciti* pogled na taj dokument kasnije. (I will take a look at that document later.)
7. Molim te da ne *bacaš* hranu. (Please don't waste food.)
8. Upravo sam *bacila* pogled na tvoju novu sliku na Instagramu. (I just took a look at your new picture on Instagram.)
9. Ova igračka ima opasne delove, ne *baci* je. (This toy has dangerous parts, don't throw it away.)
10. Uživam da *bacam* žetone dok igram rulet. (I enjoy throwing chips while playing roulette.)